\begin_inset Formula $r\in\left\{ \norm{\v x}{}\midd |\v x=\left(x_{1},x_{2},x_{3}\right)\in h\set T^{3}\wedge\frac{h}{2}\in\left\{ x_{1},x_{2},x_{3}\right\} \right\} $
